        <briefdescription>
<para>Set or clear the events in an event object. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This routine sets the events stored in event object to the specified value. All tasks waiting on the event object <emphasis>event</emphasis> whose waiting conditions become met by this immediately unpend. Unlike <ref refid="group__event__apis_1gac22e9d768d003246e68b4b0b64e60f49" kindref="member">k_event_set</ref>, this routine allows specific event bits to be set and cleared as determined by the mask.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>event</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Address of the event object </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>events</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Set of events to set/clear in <emphasis>event</emphasis> </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>events_mask</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Mask to be applied to <emphasis>events</emphasis> </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
